title: Carl Dick German Shepherd Dog with Lead 9 inches, 22cm, Plush Toy, Soft Toy, Stuffed Animal 3322
features: High quality German shepherd dog with leash. The leash is approx. 20cm long.
The plush dog stands and is approx. 22cm long. The upward pointing tail measures another 10cm. The fur has a very pleasant feel. Ideal also as decoration.
The coat of the shepherd dog is brown and black on the back, which gives the dog a lifelike look. The colour of the safety eyes is brown.
Hand washing is recommended for care. The material of the plush toy is flame-retardant, anti-allergic and manufactured according to the highest safety standards.

A product from the Carl Dick Collection. The traditional brand has been successful in the market for over 30 years and is a specialist in cuddly toys with headquarters in Garmisch-Partenkirchen, Germany.
